   ·· ·::·::·:·    /        entrance fee         /            ·::·:::·::· ·
¯ ¯ ¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯/¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯/¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯ ¯ ¯¯¯ ¯¯ ¯¯ ¯

The  entrance  fee  is  very  low  comparing to previous parties took place
during  the  WOC.   We are not that kind of people who gonna let others pay
for  our amusement.  We figured out the entrance fee and maked it as low as
possible  for  you,  that we just will be able to pay the rent of the party
place.

Entrance fee is 10,00 DM only.
------------------------------      

- Admission free for girls! -




o5                  _                             _
  __ _______________/_____________________________/________ _ __ __ __ __
   ·· ·::·::·:·    /  features and competitions  /            ·::·:::·::· ·
¯ ¯ ¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯/¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯/¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯ ¯ ¯¯¯ ¯¯ ¯¯ ¯

We  have  some  great  competitions waiting for you on that saturday night.
You  sure  will  be amused and have a lot of fun.  In advance, competitions
like  that  never  has  been  shown so far.  They are crazy and marvellous.
Also,  there  will  be a lot of prices for the competitors, and lastly some
very  interesting  special  CC98-prices, we prepared for the saturday night
show, for winners only!

You will be entertained by the scener's favorite Nr.  1 entertainer:

                        sTEELER of Phantasm

He  is  the main organizer and entertainer from the Mekka+Symposium Parties
in Falling Bostel and Hamburg, Germany.  He will be the man of the night!

The  events  and  competitions  will  start  at 9 pm (21:00 cet) during the
partyand will end about 10 pm (22:00 cet).

Don't miss the great show!




