o8                  _                             _
  __ _______________/_____________________________/________ _ __ __ __ __
   ·· ·::·::·:·    /       general rules         /            ·::·:::·::· ·
¯ ¯ ¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯/¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯/¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯ ¯ ¯¯¯ ¯¯ ¯¯ ¯

* We are not responsible for any stolen stuff at the party place.  If you
  have some articles of value you bought from the fair or something  like
  that, please  contact  the organizers and tell them to save those stuff
  for you.

* Don't scribble around or put any stickers to anywhere at the party. The
  party  place  is  at  good  condition.  We will call the police and sue
  anybody,  who  damages  any property of the party place.  We don't have
  the money to pay for any damages you cause on purpose.

* It's  not  allowed  to  bring  your own beverages into the party place.

* Don't  bring  your  computers  to  the  party. If you do it anyway, you
  should  know,  that  we  don't  have the opportunity to place computers
  around. It's up to your own responsibility.




